node.text: Movado will make donations to @alexilubomirski preferred charities in celebration of the launch: Concern Worldwide US and the Humane Society of the United States. $50 from every purchase will also be donated to the charities. Here’s Alexi on why he picked these organizations and what they mean to him.  #AlexiXMovado #Movado @humanesociety @concernworldwideus

node.text: Meet the new #Modern47. Cast in on-trend neutral tan, this timepiece combines iconic design with a cool, contemporary sand dune-inspired dial. Now available exclusively on Movado.com!

node.text: Our heart cuff and #MovadoEsperanza bangle watch are a match made in heaven. Both are available now on Movado.com. #MovadoJewelry

node.text: Style Guide: Mixing Metals. Pair our stainless steel Esperanza bracelet with the two-tone #MovadoEsperanza bangle watch for an ultra-chic look. Tap to purchase both.

node.text: Who could blame you for staring? Our Esperanza bracelet is striking in gold with its signature open vertical link bracelet. Shop it now and make it a part of your jewelry collection. #MovadoJewelry

node.text: White hot summer. This 36 mm #MovadoBOLD piece is stunning in white ceramic with a silver white dial and crystal dot detail. Tap and shop yours today.

node.text: That something extra…Add an elegant finish to your look with pieces from our jewelry collection, sold exclusively on Movado.com. Go check it out now! #MovadoJewelry

node.text: Go for gold! Elevate your wrist game with gleaming golden designs like this 42mm #MovadoBold Verso with date window detailing. Tap and shop now.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Movado on August 05, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and wrist watch.

node.text: Bold, bright, and beautiful! The #MovadoBold TR90 comes to life in stunning chartreuse, bright blue, and sporty red. A stylish black perforated leather strap adds a sleek finish. Tap and shop all three today.

node.text: Designed to turn heads! The new #MovadoBold TR90 chronographs go bold in vibrant colors and sleek minimalist styling. Head to Movado.com to see the entire collection.

node.text: Introducing the new #MovadoBold TR90. Combining modern minimalism with dynamic, automotive-inspired design. Tap the image to shop now!

node.text: It's all about function and dramatic modern design. These #MovadoBold Fusions feature stainless steel bracelets, matching dials, and ceramic bezels. Both are available now on Movado.com.

node.text: Double the Movado, double the fun! The #MovadoSE Automatic with a grey dial and gold accents pairs effortlessly with our Signature Pearl Chain Bracelet. Click to shop now. #MovadoJewelry
